txt.en: Find and defeat the Khûdi caracal matron, Amangísu, in Tir Katar.
The matron Amangísu emerges to defend her pack!
'Greetings! You made the roads safer and defeated the matron. Come, we should return to Iridír.'
'Thank you, I thought this was the end for me.'
'I can make it back on my own. I thank you stranger.'
Caracals in Tir Katar have been preying on travellers in the area. Drive them out of the area and try to find any survivors.
'You cleared the way? I will try and make my escape.'
'Do my eyes deceive me? Are you here to rescue us?'
A scout has arrived to escort you back to Iridír
Your mission is to travel to Tir Katar and put an end to the caracals who have been preying on nearby travellers and help any survivors you can find.
